The paper discusses the design of measurement matrices and recovery algorithms, which are key components of compressive sensing. These topics are typically covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Signal Processing (cs.SP), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the application of compressive sensing in image processing (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM), indicating that these sub-categories are also relevant.
